node.text:
Today’s leg day! Also did single leg glute bridges, but didn’t film them.

1. Squat 3x5
2. Squat Pt2 3x8 slow and pause at bottom
3. Backstep lunge w/ leg lift 4x8 each leg
4. Good morning 4x10
5. Single leg glute bridge 4x15 each leg
6. Wall sit 4x1 min superset skier squat 4x15

Shoes are @vivobarefoot and Reebok CrossFit lifters

node.text:
Good 🦵 day pump! Leg day is always a fave. 
I did:

1. Trap bar deadlift 4x8
2. BB RDL 4x10
3. BB walking lunges 4x20
4. BB glute bridge 4x20 (10 pulse reps, 10 regular)
5. Reverse plank holds 4x1 min (30 sec weighted, 30 sec BW)
6. Hip abductions 5x15
